@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container mt-5 pb-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10">
            <div class="text-center mb-5">
                <h1 class="fw-bold display-5 mb-3">Privacy <span style="color: var(--accent);">Policy</span></h1>
                <p class="text-muted lead">Last updated: April 2026</p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-card shadow-sm p-4 p-md-5 mb-4" style="background-color: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px;">

                <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 border-bottom border-secondary pb-2">1. Introduction</h4>
                <p class="text-muted mb-4">
                    Welcome to AssetInsight. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you visit our website and use our financial tracking, backtesting, and social features.
                </p>

                <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 border-bottom border-secondary pb-2">2. Data We Collect</h4>
                <ul class="text-muted mb-4">
                    <li class="mb-2"><strong>Account Information:</strong> When you register, we collect your First Name, Last Name, Email Address, and Username.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2"><strong>Authentication Data:</strong> If you use external authentication providers (e.g., Google), we collect basic profile data required to link your accounts safely.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2"><strong>Platform Usage:</strong> Data regarding your custom trading strategies, watchlists, posts, comments, and reactions are stored securely on our servers to provide you with your personalized dashboard.</li>
                </ul>

                <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 border-bottom border-secondary pb-2">3. How We Use Your Data</h4>
                <p class="text-muted mb-4">
                    Your data is strictly used to enhance your experience on AssetInsight. Specifically, we use it to:
                </p>
                <ul class="text-muted mb-4">
                    <li class="mb-2">Manage your account and authentication status.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Send real-time alerts and notifications regarding the stock symbols on your Watchlist.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Save and process your custom algorithmic trading strategies in our Backtest Engine.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Facilitate social interactions, such as displaying your posts to your followers.</li>
                </ul>

                <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 border-bottom border-secondary pb-2">4. Third-Party Services</h4>
                <p class="text-muted mb-4">
                    AssetInsight integrates with third-party financial APIs (such as Finnhub) to provide real-time market data and news. We do <strong>not</strong> share your personal algorithmic strategies or identifying profile data with these financial providers. Data sent to third parties is strictly limited to anonymous requests for stock ticker information.
                </p>

                <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 border-bottom border-secondary pb-2">5. Data Security & Retention</h4>
                <p class="text-muted mb-4">
                    We implement industry-standard security measures, including encrypted password storage and secure database hashing, to prevent your personal data from being accidentally lost, used, or accessed in an unauthorized way. You maintain full ownership of your data and can request deletion of your custom strategies or account at any time through your Account Settings.
                </p>

                <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 border-bottom border-secondary pb-2">6. Contact Us</h4>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">
                    If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:privacy@assetinsight.com" style="color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none;">privacy@assetinsight.com</a>.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>